    {
      "instruction": "<p>Sit the<strong> pork & beef meatballs </strong>over the <strong>grated onion</strong> in an <strong>oven-proof dish</strong> with a drizzle of<strong> olive oil</strong></p><p>Put the dish in the oven for 5-6 min or until the onion has started to soften</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-copy-29-1704446756726-x200.jpg",
