    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your<strong> spinach</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Once the meatballs are cooked, remove the dish from the oven and top with the <strong>spinach</strong></p><p>Return the dish to the oven and cook for 1-2 min further or until the spinach has started to wilt</p><p>Mix it all together – these are your <strong>baked</strong> <strong>pork & beef meatballs with tomato sauce</strong></p>",
